snippet.title: Doki Doki Blue Skies - Snow Effect
snippet.description:
Code used: https://tofurocks.itch.io/snowfall-gui. Made using the SnowBlossom function

Snow falls softly onto the streets of Japan as the MC and Natsuki go Secret Santa shopping.
